data.description: Fantastic property located outside of the City limits with no HOA's on TWO LOTS with over 20 Oak Trees. Plenty parking for your RV and/or Boat and a detached garage/shop for additional storage or parking. You'll also find another workshop for your hobbies in the backyard already setup for all your tools. Great outdoor entertainment space with a deck and covered BBQ area. The home is a 2/1 with a large open floor plan. Plenty room to add a large island for additional space. Extra storage in the half converted garage. There's no lack of storage space around this home. Located in an area where you can still golf cart to the beach, shops or to the fabulous new Art Center. Makes for a great vacation home to lock & leave or a primary residence with some small renovations to make it your own.
